strings: <voice_0x01001467><se_high>Raya: Thank you. No doubt it is the guidance of Kupas that has brought you here.
<voice_0x01001468><se_high>Raya: The only way to stop the revival of the Lord of Darkness, Rhapthorne, is to seal away the sceptre that contains him once more...
<voice_0x01001469><se_high>Raya: Please let us do what little we can to assist you.
<voice_0x0100146C><se_high>Raya: I want these people to have Kupas's great treasure. Would you go and let the guard know?
<voice_0x0100146E><se_high>Raya: As you just heard, I wish to give you something from our gully's treasure chamber.
<voice_0x0100146F><se_high>Raya: It's called the Darktree leaf and it belonged to Kupas. It's the leaf from a giant tree that exists in the World of Darkness.
<voice_0x01001470><se_high>Raya: People say that, if you place it on a map, it will instantly show you the location of a great evil.

<voice_0x01001471><se_high>Raya: The fate of the world is in your hands.
We're all depending on you. We will await
news of your success here in the gully.
